cs.SI, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.SD, cs.CL

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the project focuses on analyzing data from a social platform, Instagram. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the project involves analyzing Instagram filters and their relationship with the number of likes. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the project involves analyzing popular hashtags in different locations. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the project may involve developing software tools for data analysis. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also a possible category as the project may involve natural language processing for analyzing captions and comments on Instagram posts.
